example.para:
Notice how the angle brackets in the
	    #include line need to be referenced by their
	    entities instead of being included literally.

example.programlisting:
#include <stdio.h>

int
main(void)
{
    printf("hello, world\n");
}

#include <stdio.h> 

int 
main(void)
{
    printf("hello, world\n"); 
}
